Module com.example.project3
Package com.example.project3

Class ClassSchedule

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3.ClassSchedule
public class ClassSchedule
extends java.lang.Object
The Schedule class manages all the fitness classes at the gym. Schedule contains a list of all the fitness classes and includes methods to detect time conflicts, check if a class is offered at the gym, get FitnessClass objects, and print the schedule of classes.
Author:
Jackson Lee, Serena Zeng
